friendly_name: Fake LinkedIn Profile or Email Login Template
comments: ["This seems to be a template targeting Chinese-speaking users of LinkedIn and 163.com's email site. In the former
references: the template shows what looks like LinkedIn's site with a particular user's profile showing and a prompt to reauthenticate to the site. It's unclear whether the initial lure is a connection request or something else
author: as the profile used repeatedly in this template doesn't look like a connection request. In the latter case
brands_targeted: the prompt is the same but the background is a 163.com email inbox."]

comments: ['This seems to be a template targeting AT&T customers. The template focuses on convincing a user that their billing information is somehow wrong
